      "stem_html": "<p>Fill in the missing reagents <b>a</b>–<b>e</b> in the following scheme:</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBa1VaIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--a94adbce357286a360dad51e0670d62684b73428/OChem_24_EC_044.jpg\" alt=\"Acetophenone reacts with a to form 1-phenylethanamine. This reacts with b and c to form styrene. This reacts with d to form 2-phenyloxirane. This reacts with e to form 2-(dimethylamino)-1-phenylethanol.\">",
